WEBVTT

1
00:02:58.190 --> 00:03:01.230 
惨遭蒙面懦夫们的毒手
butchered by cowards who hide behind masks.

2
00:03:02.740 --> 00:03:05.340 
达里奥·纳哈里斯次子团团长丹妮莉丝的情人

3
00:03:03.860 --> 00:03:06.480 
我们可以后撤到金字塔区
We could pull back to the pyramid district,

4
00:03:06.480 --> 00:03:09.820 
把那清场 将之作为行动的大本营
secure it, and use it as a base from which to operate.

5
00:03:09.820 --> 00:03:12.990 
然后我们肃清整个城市
Then we clean the city out,

6
00:03:13.040 --> 00:03:16.890 
逐街逐巷搜个底朝天
neighborhood by neighborhood, street by street,

7
00:03:16.930 --> 00:03:19.190 
直到鼠辈们无处藏身
until the rats have nowhere left to hide.

8
00:03:19.140 --> 00:03:21.440 
西茨达拉·佐·洛拉克弥林贵族

9
00:03:23.050 --> 00:03:25.670 
我更喜欢你之前的建议
I prefer your earlier suggestion.

10
00:03:25.670 --> 00:03:29.500 
把弥林城所有大家族的族长都抓起来带给我
Round up the leaders of each of Meereen's great families and bring them to me.

